 a nation or a kingdom that I will build and plant it. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 1:10","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 1:10","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:18:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"However, if it does what is evil in my sight by not listening to me, I will relent concerning the good I had said I would do to it. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 18:25–29","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 33:12–13","book":"Ezk","chapter":33,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 18:25–29","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":25},{"label":"Ezk 33:12–13","book":"Ezk","chapter":33,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:18:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So now, say to the men of Judah and to the residents of Jerusalem, ‘This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: Look, I am about to bring harm to you and make plans against you. Turn now, each from your evil way, and correct your ways and your deeds.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:18","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:3","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 4:18","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":18},{"label":"Jr 7:3","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:18:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But they will say, ‘It’s hopeless. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 57:12","book":"Isa","chapter":57,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:25","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"ki